INSTALLATION!

make sure to download and setup InteractSound as this is needed for the AI voice. Make sure to name the folder InteractSound
https://github.com/plunkettscott/interact-sound

Download this resource and place the afk.ogg in the InteractSound/client/html/sounds folder

And then add this resource to your server as you would like any other.
